{
  "texts": [
    "This highlights the importance of security measures that ensure privacy by protecting critical medical assets.",
    "Moreover, providing the ethical conduct of research with human participants requires a strong emphasis on privacy and security.",
    "The Declaration of Helsinki mandates researchers engaged in medical research to uphold the confidentiality and security of the personal information of research subjects [36].",
    "Besides, protecting data privacy is a vital requirement for data sharing in clinical trials while making data available for further research [37].",
    "Clinical research often requires data sharing among healthcare organizations."
  ]
}